:"2019-06-19T11:08:33.000Z","msg":"票你老母"},{"pid":"dfcf4b5bce2a9b8ec313a500b092371874f418b0","tid":1243132,"uid":35221,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e5cc1cf7e2ece619b5cce314fa9eca9bf1b0530a","tid":1243132,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41b39af329d26c50fde97f489bc7b0389032bf24","tid":1243132,"uid":35221,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"4512a10d5205bd714c90604ba88020e89a63d1e1","tid":1243132,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:55:22.000Z","msg":"睇翻鄭立篇文 我覺得仲可接受<br />\n但寫到明 血債票償 真係好難睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:58:10.000Z","msg":"犯民個私心根本就係其中一個主要分化源頭<br />\n<br />\n階段性勝利：而家根本毫無勝利；林卓廷講5:0就凸顯曬呢班仆街啲真面目<br />\n拿拿淋收割成果：而家根本毫無成果<br />\n畀啲掌聲自己：歌頌遊行人數<br />\n食人血饅頭：烈士頭七都未過就血債票償，呢個我真係屌佢老母臭屄<br />\n而家犯民又做齊曬雨革之後啲仆街嘢<br />\n<br />\n而家夠票喇，梗係收工，永續議席、永續出糧<br />\n錢就我犯民袋，烈士啲血就你流<br />\n血債血償？唔關我犯民事架喇，咪撚搞到我選舉添呀<br />\n跟住再一句車埋嚟話你分化撚，立於永遠不敗之道德高地，本土港獨繼續淪為condom，真係好撚嘢<br />\n<br />\n從來冇人旨意過犯民要幫我哋衝，都話咗各有各做，鄺朱區而家支援就係佢哋應該要做嘅嘢<br />\n但係講乜撚嘢血債票償就正仆街冚家剷，完全自私<br />\n我哋當犯民係同路人，犯民有冇當過我哋係同路人又另一回事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:03:21.000Z","msg":"巴打 絕對理解你不滿 <br />\n但可惜香港依一刻 仲需要佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有頭髮邊個想做幟哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唉 屌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:11:54.000Z","msg":"其實佢哋唔再backstab，唔再割𥱊，唔再篤灰，我已經好感激。我對呢班犯民一早已經絕望甚至無感。而家2019年喇，已經係全面開戰，都重講乜撚嘢立法會關鍵一席真係笑話<br />\n<br />\n但係而家屌你老母打緊仗吖嘛，就已經講選選選。而家係乜鳩都攞唔到，就已經個個爭住出嚟食人血饅頭，係咪人嚟架呢啲<br />\n<br />\n跟住你屌佢兩句唔好講乜撚嘢血債票償，佢重夠膽死用返個話語權嚟屌柒返你做分化撚，霸道咪就係呢啲囉。係，大是大非，我當你係同路人，得。但恐怕都係又一次痴心錯付，因為你犯民始終都係冇當過我哋係同路人，仍然都係為自己，咁究竟邊個分化邊個？"},{"pid":"cef6086516b7e05b4f1425776442f348f8e4e6f8","tid":1243132,"uid":107833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e8390961bb411f39ecf12c6a813a172b2e274b8","tid":1243132,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T10:57:19.000Z","msg":"如果救唔到 我投番民賤算啦 <br />\n反正都冇得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:17:07.000Z","msg":"睇完上次台灣選巿長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我認為巴打要三思"},{"pid":"c71f215fd5ba5672e42cbeabe9019dc4faca04d5","tid":1243132,"uid":157994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:57:26.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"d82dec4950ca66d5b79d2108ab2806d83ca7f26d","tid":1243132,"uid":52283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:03:14.000Z","msg":"一定要傾定點樣配票"},{"pid":"af384cad97fafce5cd9ecfaa90afda58e751d78b","tid":1243132,"uid":126668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:04:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"886c61cde5e69dcb2898f8efe2b6b9acc1dea7cb","tid":1243132,"uid":36321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:04:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6e0002183a62975ffc138a5d8466d808bc2be934","tid":1243132,"uid":219211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:04:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cda706040c9caf2c245a0de111fd886ab07763e9","tid":1243132,"uid":36321,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:05:18.000Z","msg":"唔該 真心出少句聲當幫忙 大家已經一頭煙 冇時間再分心<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60100528ef7f4dd665dc9324d949b6563129dab0","tid":124313